{"tid":686223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［大勝!！］越南禁止境內使用支付寶、微信支付","createTime":"2018-06-01T05:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T05:23:05.000Z","uid":48083,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"73c54f039558f01b892ddbf1d37b353d8b0bc6c0","tid":686223,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/130832_c4cacf9374fa2b7941934a79e3bd3955.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F130832_c4cacf9374fa2b7941934a79e3bd3955.png&h=c3d94c43&s={SIZE}\" />近日，越南金融管理機構宣佈，將著手整頓越南境內的電子支付市場，更直指支付寶、微信支付和POS機人民幣刷卡結賬為「非法支付結算」。<br />\n<br />\n受此影響，當地已經在使用中國移動支付的商戶相繼撤下支付寶、微信支付等標識和廣告。當地有商戶表示支付寶從去年底進入越南，早前並未被認定為非法，現只運行半年就被叫停。<br />\n<br />\n據越媒報導，有越南金融機構人士透露，支付寶、微信支付已導致越南外匯管理方面的問題和稅收流失，這是叫停的一個重要原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=10823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D10823&d=N%2BywAU3rtOvD%2FF0MpcDFvqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8046017a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=10823</a>"},{"pid":"48ee2734961fe5be65f76e5a04549a03a0181407","tid":686223,"uid":164372,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/130944_dde459c0ab53a8a410f75ca0a7d1722b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F130944_dde459c0ab53a8a410f75ca0a7d1722b.png&h=49edbdb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"068cf293cb7a6c0e8c7c5967d1269bcde6bf28a8","tid":686223,"uid":3510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"亮劍！！！"},{"pid":"ea7bcc668462ea761a6424049270367df78b554b","tid":686223,"uid":135132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"中國或成（略"},{"pid":"1af6beeadd3a214c3ffc62d3b06a10446f3d912f","tid":686223,"uid":182314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:16:00.000Z","msg":"抵制越南，中國或會成為最大贏家"},{"pid":"041438192ef23f46c432a923fa52a35a728655f8","tid":686223,"uid":183302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"越南未富先驕 越南會被邊緣化"},{"pid":"d7b7627f3e0cb7a3b301224fc0f80bdbc068376e","tid":686223,"uid":92859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"越南使用支付寶：支付寶擴展業務至越南，中國成最大贏家<br />\n<br />\n越南禁用支付寶：中國科技領先，中國成最大贏家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立於不敗之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c08333b8674c779951b0c317761c1c78ec2027","tid":686223,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068cf293cb7a6c0e8c7c5967d1269bcde6bf28a8","tid":686223,"uid":3510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"亮劍！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"回鞘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3889fc1e2469ba20f491ce49d240564af92d6f9","tid":686223,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:03:25.000Z","msg":"未見五毛蹤影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd84f724eda90904c73e280cca68c6c7bdcd5636","tid":686223,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"中國一定贏到開巷"},{"pid":"c7eeef7de1bc291db36c68d59c4cc95186eeea09","tid":686223,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"越南未能使用最先進的支付方法，必會對經濟構成毁滅性衝擊，中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"ac324d2b3477555979793faa52574b8bbe2bdb8a","tid":686223,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"支金去晒大陸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac327ac16ff38857001af8d753804bd558b871b2","tid":686223,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"